  "tips": [
    {
      "type": "lead",
      "text": "You can type every letter now. Time for the marks that make copy readable. The period and the comma do more honest work than any other keys on the board - one stops a thought, the other lets it breathe. Get these right and your sentences stop running into each other."
    },
    {
      "type": "drop",
      "text": "Both live on the bottom row, no Shift required. The period sits under your right ring finger; the comma under your right middle. Reach straight down from L and K, tap, and bring the finger home. Keep the rest of the hand on its keys - you are nudging two fingers, not lifting the whole hand."
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "icon": "✍️",
      "title": "Space after, never before",
      "text": "One space follows a period or comma; nothing comes before it. \"yes, it works\" - not \"yes ,it works\". That single habit separates clean copy from clutter, so build it in now."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": ". . . . . . . . . . . . . . .",
      "finger": "orange",
      "title": "The period",
      "hint": "Right ring finger drops to the period, then back home. Steady, even taps."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": ", , , , , , , , , , , , , , ,",
      "finger": "orange",
      "title": "The comma",
      "hint": "Right middle finger drops to the comma, then home. No hurry."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Two marks under control. Now put them to work in real sentences, where the pause matters as much as the words. Read each line whole, then type it - period to stop, comma to breathe, one space after each."
    },
    {
      "type": "pullquote",
      "text": "Accuracy is respect - for the word, for the reader, and for yourself.",
      "by": "Eleanor Hayes, editor"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "yes, it works. she said, this is fine. then, we go. ready, set, type, and breathe.",
      "finger": "green",
      "title": "Real sentences",
      "hint": "Mind the spacing: space after every period and comma, never before."
    },
    {
